ðŸ”· Encoder
ðŸ”¹ What it is:
A combinational circuit that encodes a one-hot input into an n-bit binary output.
ðŸ”¹ Structure:
Inputs: 2â¿
Outputs: n
ðŸ”¸ Problems:
